| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0832 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2553aa07-da60-5d1e-8c5f-e4dd1e2c7ba0"
